# Allowlist for `podman build .` -- the Dockerfile only COPYs four
# files, so anything else in the build context is wasted bytes (and
# `terraform/.terraform` is a symlink pointing outside the repo, which
# trips podman's symlink check at context-load time). Pattern: exclude
# everything, then re-include the specific paths each COPY needs. Add
# new entries here whenever the Dockerfile gets a new COPY.
*
!mise.toml
!pyproject.toml
!uv.lock
!packer
packer/*
!packer/qemu.pkr.hcl
